description: Monthly arts and culture newspaper in Canada
label: The Overcast
title: The_Overcast
exrest: The Overcast is a monthly newspaper that covers arts and culture in St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador. The paper began publishing in February 2014, founded by St. John's author and blogger Chad Pelley.
